服務時間<br />\n原來武漢肺炎先係最強暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39c7a3fc11e15d08d54074ce68fd746c2a3168c","tid":1891531,"uid":3818,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"可加可減機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加價減班次"},{"pid":"707c15885d4e32a02711f3fc2c76842e5d339df1","tid":1891531,"uid":85629,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁佢減價未</span>"},{"pid":"7a7966899822269557a455ef79d120bdbf337f06","tid":1891531,"uid":274363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d601ab3c4aa36ed864b49ca35f55874872519352","tid":1891531,"uid":325869,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"人手又減、班次都減。淨係班垃圾高層唔減人工，咁既環境車費都唔減，咁我真係唔知幾時可以減，當香港冇人住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ca96eb7bf76542cbdbd7055afa45036da4578b","tid":1891531,"uid":335434,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"索性用「配合警方行動」做理由全部線停駛半年咪得囉 又唔係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544a3cad11818d5a45dc66286b1995d4059c520f","tid":1891531,"uid":59633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"都無人搭架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342b0d9650c0fe1d799406d4648e673a9b662566","tid":1891531,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707c15885d4e32a02711f3fc2c76842e5d339df1","tid":1891531,"uid":85629,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-l